Yuliya Nikolaevna Chizhenko-Fomenko (Russian: Юлия Николаевна Чиженко-Фоменко, amụrụ n'abalị iri atọ na ọnwa Ọgọstụ n'afọ 1979) bụ onye Russia na-agba ọsọ n'etiti etiti nke bụ ọkachamara na mita 1500.
Na 2005 World Championships ọ mechiri na ọkwa ọlaọcha n'azụ Tatyana Tomashova, mana a chụpụrụ ya maka igbochi Maryam Yusuf Jamal nke Bahrain
N'afọ sochirinụ Chizhenko meriri World Indoor Championships tupu ọ bụrụ onye nke abụọ na 2006 European Athletics Championships, ọzọ n'azụ Tomashova.

A họpụtara Fomenko ka ọ nọchite anya Russia na 2008 Summer Olympics, mana kemgbe ahụ ka a machiri ya na asọmupi n'ihi mmebi nke ule doping, yana ndị egwuregwu Russia isii ndị ọzọ, gụnyere Tomashova na Yelena Soboleva.
N'abalị iri abụọ na ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 2008, a mara ọkwa na Fomenko na ndị egwuregwu Russia isii ndị ọzọ ga-enweta mmachibido iwu doping afọ abụọ maka iji ọgwụ ọjọọ mee ihe.
